subtitle: GTA+ Classics Collection
content:
GTA+ Members can claim a host of gifts through May 28:

— The Principe Deveste Eight (Super) with a free HSW Upgrade
— The HSW Orange Trip and HSW CMYK Glitch liveries for the Deveste Eight
— Off White Pearl Chameleon Paint and Off White Pearl Chameleon Wheel Paint
— LS Customs Neck Gaiter
— Gray Yeti Combat Shirt and Battle Pants
— Gold Beat Off Earphones

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
